<section>
	<title>Workspace concept</title>
	<para>A workspace is a specific space that contains all
		administration actions. This space is also considered as the private
		one where users can choose their favorite and frequently used gadgets
		to meet their need of daily works and activities as well as helps them
		access and perform actions easily, quickly and effectively. You can
		see this workspace in the illustration below:</para>
